  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I take a pen-- a pen-- and I put them against their head and I said, OK, this is a gun.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How are you going to fight me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I know it's very crude, but it works.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "OK, you had one choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Weapons, you didn't have, I didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So how would you attack the guy that stands down there, that's well fed, that's strong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe he's stupid, but he has all these facilities with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "What are you go-- how are you going to attack him?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "By scratching his eyes out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Or knocking him on the chin?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he kills you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So what have you achieved?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the tough part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in-- after the horse has left the barn, we can all be smart asses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and-- and-- and all the people that are-- that are writing books, and theories, about what is this, and what is that, and shoot this, and shoot that, hey, after the war, I know we shouldn't touch this, but very briefly, I want to--",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
